Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.74,0:12:45.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪欧你要继续独自战斗吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.61,0:12:46.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.98,0:12:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其他人在哪里做什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.68,0:12:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只好自己行动啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.28,0:12:54.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我做得到的，你仅管说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.89,0:12:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我什么也会帮你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.29,0:12:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.29,0:13:00.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,晚餐你可以弄牛排给我吃吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.96,0:13:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是，我是认真的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.83,0:13:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.36,0:13:08.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在这样已经足够
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.50,0:13:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是什么呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.27,0:13:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.34,0:13:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢…钢弹?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.48,0:13:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.82,0:13:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪欧‧麦斯威尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.79,0:13:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乖乖地跟我来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.86,0:13:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反抗就会当场没命啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.70,0:13:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,随你喜欢啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.43,0:13:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但那支雷射炮很强力啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.90,0:13:49.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果这卫星化成飞灰\N也没问题吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.27,0:13:51.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要紧啊   什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.28,0:13:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这种地方变成怎样也和我无关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.91,0:13:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不想只是做一个技师军官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.28,0:14:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要能解开这部钢弹系统之谜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.82,0:14:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兹巴洛夫特校的MD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.75,0:14:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就会成为落后的无用之物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.52,0:14:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新的OZ需要新的系统
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.89,0:14:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了那目的，我什么事也会做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.86,0:14:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来这里!钢弹驾驶员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.07,0:14:18.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要的只是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.35,0:14:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然要我戴上古怪的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.99,0:14:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想我做什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.36,0:14:45.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用这部飞翼零式和MD战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.26,0:14:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当然是用实弹啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.80,0:14:51.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无所谓\N但我或许会中途逃走啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.57,0:14:53.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你做不到啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.40,0:14:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已经把飞翼零式改为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.01,0:14:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能从外面停止机能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.74,0:14:59.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.28,0:15:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你有任何异常举动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.28,0:15:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MD的攻击目标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.15,0:15:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就会变成那个卫星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.39,0:15:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.80,0:15:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果在这位置用来福枪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.60,0:15:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卫星就会有损毁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.60,0:15:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.87,0:15:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错，就那样战斗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.58,0:15:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的眼看见什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.65,0:15:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让我看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.85,0:15:44.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.86,0:15:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.93,0:15:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你果然也看见吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.50,0:15:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，回答我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.96,0:15:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飞翼零式想让驾驶员看见什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.47,0:15:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这种东西我怎知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.04,0:16:04.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错!我的对手是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.76,0:16:21.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.22,0:17:23.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么回事…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.99,0:17:27.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我究竟做过什么…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.74,0:17:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎…怎会的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.52,0:18:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这种事…人类…怎么做得到…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.56,0:18:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做得到啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.03,0:18:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,应该做得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.26,0:18:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人类的意识改革后…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.26,0:18:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，在改变潮流的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.37,0:18:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,划时代系统之下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.20,0:18:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本没有不可能的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.81,0:18:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特兰特特尉!你听到吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.31,0:18:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乖乖地把飞翼零式交给我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.51,0:18:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后投降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.54,0:18:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是兹巴洛夫特校的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.85,0:18:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重覆!把飞翼零式交给我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.32,0:18:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后投降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.69,0:18:31.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.42,0:18:36.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要消灭他们啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.76,0:18:41.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停止，特兰特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.53,0:18:43.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那系统…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.64,0:18:48.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪欧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.61,0:18:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是飞翼零式!它一直飞过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.84,0:18:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兹巴洛夫特校!要俘虏它吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.31,0:18:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,消灭它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.61,0:18:59.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.89,0:19:04.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特兰特这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.93,0:19:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还没，还没能看见一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.43,0:19:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来，尽情放马过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.80,0:19:18.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要去!迪欧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.94,0:19:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你那身体状况不能战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.57,0:19:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别担心…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.27,0:19:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是钢弹的驾驶员啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.25,0:19:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那系统不是人类能驾御的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.95,0:19:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我无论如何要制止他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.50,0:19:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不断扩张
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.97,0:19:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的意识不断扩张啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.94,0:19:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还差一点就能看见一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.57,0:19:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还差一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.39,0:20:13.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还没，还不够
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.82,0:20:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还不够啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.46,0:20:18.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.50,0:20:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,速度很快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.57,0:20:25.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我能看见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.64,0:20:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我能清楚看见你的动作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.41,0:20:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,连你死去的模样也能看见啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.61,0:20:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混帐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.82,0:20:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,连力量也是对方占优势吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.69,0:20:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.53,0:20:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大笨蛋，你还不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.00,0:20:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,靠力量赢不了我吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.47,0:20:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.77,0:21:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你死在这里\N而我就抓紧荣耀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.31,0:21:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要看过才知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.61,0:21:05.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.71,0:21:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有招叫同归于尽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.25,0:21:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.55,0:21:18.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不会输…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.82,0:21:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我怎会输给你这种人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.26,0:21:23.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不是输给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.86,0:21:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而是输给飞翼零式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.80,0:21:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我没理由会输
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.47,0:21:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你还不明白吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.28,0:21:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不会输，没理由会输
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.11,0:21:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不会输给区区这种系统…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.30,0:22:03.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人类做不到那种事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.40,0:22:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果有人做得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.64,0:22:07.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是超越人类的生物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.71,0:22:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待续
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.76,0:22:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心血来潮的找人出来\N只因为天气好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.76,0:22:38.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让我一直等不到人\N你以为你是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.76,0:22:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道你是跑过来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.76,0:22:46.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但那也是应该的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.26,0:22:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Just Love ! 那个惹人厌的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.76,0:23:01.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捉弄人  是因为心理有爱意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.26,0:23:09.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Just Love !  老是让人挂念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.76,0:23:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起\N我不该说出强人所难的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.76,0:23:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,‧‧‧Just Love‧‧‧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.55,0:23:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,次回予告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.26,0:23:34.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯‧马吉斯再次戴起面具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.53,0:23:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不断消灭罗姆斐拉的MD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.63,0:23:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讨厌这种行动的迪尔麦优候爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.36,0:23:41.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,召见莉莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.77,0:23:44.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,质问她他是否支援米利亚尔特‧匹斯克拉福特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.44,0:23:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,另一方面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.54,0:23:48.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,察知歼灭特列斯派作战的希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.31,0:23:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,独自前往最有可能战死的战场
